Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:12.15,OP Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H005BFF&}kami ni kaitara wakaru no kana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:18.28,OP Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H005BFF&}kotoba ni sureba mieru no kana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:24.12,OP Title,,0000,0000,0000,,nani mo nakunatte shimatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:29.88,OP Title,,0000,0000,0000,,dakedo karada omoku kanjita
